// ============================================================
// inject_rtti_err_set_bad_property.lox — SET undefined property
// ============================================================
// Setup: Delphi injects a TCustomer as global 'cust'.
//
// What this tests:
//   - Writing to a property that doesn't exist on TCustomer via RTTI
//   - VM should produce runtime error: "Undefined or read-only property 'Bogus'."
print cust.Name; // expect: Alice
cust.Bogus = "oops"; // expect runtime error: Undefined or read-only property 'Bogus'.
